{
  "texts": [
    "a, Tanner graph of a surface code, for comparison.",
    "b, Tanner graph of a BB code with parameters [[144, 12, 12]] embedded into a torus.",
    "Any edge of the Tanner graph connects a data and a check vertex.",
    "Data qubits associated with the registers q(L) and q(R) are shown by blue and orange circles.",
    "Each vertex has six incident edges including four short-range edges (pointing north, south, east and west) and two long-range edges."
  ]
}